# Comment widget — project rule

A Figma-style commenting overlay for live web designs. Drop one `<script>` tag onto any preview URL; stakeholders click elements to leave pinned, threaded comments; comments sync in real time. Source of truth for the spec: [`comment-widget-build-plan.md`](../../comment-widget-build-plan.md).

## How to keep this rule fresh

This rule is the **canonical project status document**. Whenever you (the agent or a human) ship something material, update the relevant section here before declaring the task done. Specifically:

- **Phase landed → flip status table** + add bullets under "What's done" + remove from "Roadmap."
- **New gotcha discovered → add to "Gotchas paid for in time"** so the next agent doesn't re-pay.
- **Convention change → update "Conventions"** and propagate to existing code if needed.
- **Release ritual change → update "Release flow."**

Keep this file under ~200 lines. If a section is getting long, factor it into its own `.mdc` rule and link.

